<i> ♪ Would you say I'm a</i>
<i> hero, glorious and brave ♪</i>

17:38.220 --> 17:43.060
<i> ♪ If I told you something</i>
<i> you wouldn't believe? ♪</i>

17:44.500 --> 17:50.820
<i> ♪ That sometimes I'm scared</i>
<i> and I can make mistakes ♪</i>

17:51.300 --> 17:57.760
<i> ♪ And I'm not so</i>
<i> heroic, it seems ♪</i>

