<i> ♪ Would you say I'm a</i>
<i> hero, glorious and brave ♪</i>

19:00.780 --> 19:05.600
<i> ♪ If I told you something</i>
<i> you wouldn't believe? ♪</i>

19:07.280 --> 19:13.480
<i> ♪ This Changeling it</i>
<i> seems, knows the real me. ♪</i>

19:14.220 --> 19:21.180
<i> ♪ And would stay by my</i>
<i> side till the end. ♪</i>

19:21.300 --> 19:24.700
<i>♪ So if day can turn to night ♪</i>

19:24.840 --> 19:28.480
<i> ♪ And the darkness</i>
<i> turn to light ♪</i>

19:28.560 --> 19:31.380
<i> ♪ Then why can't we imagine? ♪</i>

19:31.780 --> 19:38.100
<i> ♪ Just why can't we imagine,</i>
<i> then why can't we imagine ♪</i>

19:38.160 --> 19:41.920
<i> ♪ the Changeling can change? ♪</i>

19:58.380 --> 20:00.740
Spike, I'm so
proud of you.

20:00.820 --> 20:01.500
You are?

20:01.660 --> 20:04.920
Of course! You're a celebrity
here in the Crystal Empire

20:05.100 --> 20:07.140
and you just risked
all of it for a friend.

20:07.600 --> 20:10.120
I can't imagine anything
more brave than that.

20:11.260 --> 20:12.820
As the Princess of Friendship,

20:12.920 --> 20:15.640
I try to set an example
for all of Equestria.

20:15.820 --> 20:19.550
But today, it was Spike who
taught me that a new friend

20:19.600 --> 20:22.420
can come from anywhere.
I guess everypony

20:22.460 --> 20:25.420
still has things to learn
about friendship, even me.

20:25.760 --> 20:29.460
And if Spike says Thorax is his
friend, then he's my friend too.

20:31.960 --> 20:33.460
Thank you.

20:33.900 --> 20:38.020
On behalf of the Crystal Empire,
I would like to extend my hoof

20:38.040 --> 20:41.000
in friendship and I am
sure all of my subjects

20:41.040 --> 20:42.720
are eager to do the same.

20:52.710 --> 20:55.280
Welcome to the Crystal
Empire, Thorax.

20:55.540 --> 20:57.900
I'm sorry we didn't take the
time to get to know you.

20:58.360 --> 21:00.020
Maybe we can change that now.

21:00.780 --> 21:04.480
That'd be so amazing! I want
to know all about friendship.

21:04.580 --> 21:06.990
And maybe one day I can
take that knowledge back

21:07.060 --> 21:08.260
to the Changeling Kingdom.

21:08.580 --> 21:11.820
If my kind learned how to
create love for one another,

21:12.100 --> 21:14.100
maybe they wouldn't have
to take it from others!

21:14.600 --> 21:16.560
To Spike the Brave and Glorious!

21:25.140 --> 21:26.880
Looks like you were
right after all.

21:27.020 --> 21:27.960
Right about what?

21:28.120 --> 21:30.960
Friendship lessons
can happen anywhere.
